Comment: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:43.00,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we suffocate, let's yell. Ho!!!
Comment: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.14,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,In the midnight dream.
Comment: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:48.11,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,No place to relax in the sleepless city.
Comment: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:52.05,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,We smile without dropping our guard.
Comment: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:56.16,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe to lie and the truth is empty.
Comment: 0,0:00:56.16,0:01:00.21,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,I desperately wanna shut and break out.
Comment: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:02.09,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we gotta start.  Let's get moving.
Comment: 0,0:01:02.09,0:01:03.83,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move into the brand new world.
Comment: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:06.09,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dive into the brand new trip.
Comment: 0,0:01:06.09,0:01:09.81,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You're afraid of a big world.
Comment: 0,0:01:09.81,0:01:12.11,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just begun.
Comment: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:14.08,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we go full speed and funky beat.
Comment: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:15.81,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll surely shine.
Comment: 0,0:01:15.81,0:01:17.71,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Around the world.
Comment: 0,0:01:17.71,0:01:18.66,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Trip to the world.
Comment: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:20.56,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Here we go to an unknown world.
Comment: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:22.31,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a newborn traveler.
Comment: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.36,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Unstable footsteps are fun to watch.
Comment: 0,0:01:24.36,0:01:26.46,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Get things done right, only when needed.
Comment: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:27.98,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,So many people in this world...
Comment: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:30.28,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...sometimes, you'll receive slanders.
Comment: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:32.32,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's warp uninteresting things...
Comment: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.81,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...and lead at least a rational life.
Comment: 0,0:01:33.81,0:01:35.59,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our law.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:43.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm frustrated to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:48.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I want to go to Mt. Akina so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:55.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I don't know if I like to drive\Nthat much or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:02:01.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But I've been driving alone for five years,\Nwhether it was snowing or raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:04.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I've driven Akina more than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:16.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's what this is all about,\Nso let me use the car, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.93,0:02:20.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better hurry, Takumi.\NIt's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:25.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There!\NThere he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:28.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Oh no, they found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:32.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:33.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'll be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:54.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Itsuki,\Nsitting in the middle of the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:57.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta...Ta...Ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:03:00.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my way.\NI'm gonna run over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:06.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:08.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:11.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:14.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:19.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Road Racers have to accept\Nchallenges, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.50,0:03:22.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!\NHey...
