Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:04:00.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He must've gotten his license recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:06.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}How could a kid like him\Nhave such techniques?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.48,0:04:11.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I thought he'd be older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}So that's the GT-R.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:24.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}It's far better than good.\NIt's totally overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:29.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}It's got a drive train that combines the\Nadvantages of both FR and 4WD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:33.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nakazato of the Night Kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:38.54,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujiwara Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remember your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:43.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:56.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Severe understeering is better during acceleration\Nif the driver is good, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If the characteristics\Nhave changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't you think he'll get confused\Nwhen he attacks hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:05.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've told him about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't help, even if I told him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:14.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not smart enough to change his driving\Nhabits by thinking about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Say what?  Then he'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.  Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not smart...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but his physical responses are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:31.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late if you respond to thinking\Nbased on feelings in the seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:35.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Your hands and feet have to respond unconsciously\Nto control the drift, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.15,0:05:38.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:43.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,His sense of accelerating the car\Nwhile skidding is exceptional.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:47.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the suspension settings are\Na little different, it won't bother him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:50.95,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}He'll easily find the best way\Nand fully control the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:54.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}The Eight-Six is the kind of car\Nthat can train the driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:05.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the finish line.\NNo other cars are around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Anytime is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Iketani, start when you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:11.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:15.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start the countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten seconds till start!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll let you observe this battle\Nfrom the VIP seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, it's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Five seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:40.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:41.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:43.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.88,0:06:53.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The 32 has the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But Takumi isn't too far behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:02.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Put on your seatbelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.28,0:07:12.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the FC.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:14.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi Ryosuke rocket-started his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:16.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna follow them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:19.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My god, it's gonna be a super\Nbattle between the three?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:23.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be the match to determine\Nthe fastest in Gunma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:37.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That GT-R driver isn't flooring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:42.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Is he waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It wouldn't be fair to get\Na lead on the straightaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I want a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:52.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The real start is the corner's entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:05.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakazato is going easy on the pedal,\Nand waiting for the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:09.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he won't regret this easygoing attitude\Nduring the second half of the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:17.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first corner!\NThree cars are coming in back to back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:32.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Incredible.  It's just\Nlike Bunta said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.65,0:08:34.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:36.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:40.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't be able to follow me with\Nthat overly active "crab walk."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.46,0:09:15.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching him up close,\Nhis drift is almost an art form.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:19.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Four wheel drift at full throttle with\Nminimum counter steering...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:22.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how great that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:29.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He can control his Eight-Six like his arms\Nand legs in a critical situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:33.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't control my FC like he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:38.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nakazato is slowly pulling away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:45.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he be able to win this battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}This is it.\NThis is the feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.68,0:09:54.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}This high tension of boiling blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}This is a battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'll push myself to the limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:00.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}How much longer can\Nyou keep up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's different...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:19.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The car's running slightly different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:21.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The car doesn't lose stability...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:24.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...and I can depress the gas pedal early.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:29.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Dad must've done something\Nwhile I was working...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.36,0:10:32.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...because it wasn't like\Nthis earlier this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:37.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I see.  That's why he wasn't home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:42.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I don't know why, but I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The car doesn't skid too much,\Nso I can step on it without worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:56.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.21,0:10:58.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable drift!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:15.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen someone who\Ncan let their car skid on a straightaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:20.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unusual.  You can't do that unless\Nthe car maintains its speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:25.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the kind of\Ndrift we're used to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:28.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!  Once you've seen it,\Nyou won't forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:57.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}The Eight-Six is still\Nkeeping up with the 32!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:02.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi seems to be able to\Nkeep up with the 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:11.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He can match Nakazato of Myogi and\Nthe superstar, Takahashi Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:13.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's too good to be my best friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.58,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:23.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of Takahashi Ryosuke,\Nhis FC isn't part of the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:26.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a third person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Nakazato is the opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.41,0:12:32.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know he's at a disadvantage\Nracing the 32...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:34.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but since it's Takumi,\Nhe'll win, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:59.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pulling away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:03.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakazato's good enough\Nto match his big mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:08.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's balancing the load well,\Nand coping with understeering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:11.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a driving technique to make\Nuse of the power of the GT-R.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.12,0:13:14.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks boring, but he doesn't drive wastefully,\Ngiving no overtaking opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:18.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brother, how can\Nyou be so laid-back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:22.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If he wins, we'll be disgraced.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:28.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In the first half, the straightaways are relatively\Nlong, and the slopes are gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many disadvantageous\Nfactors for the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:33.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,From here, the slopes\Nwill be steeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:36.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The downhill specialist\Nwill show his true skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:58.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The 32 is good at these\Nlow speed hairpin curves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:01.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If I make use of the powerful brakes\Nand slow down as I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.20,0:14:09.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The load shifts to the front\Non the downhill...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:12.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...so it doesn't exhibit understeering\Non acceleration.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:17.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}And the acceleration in the lower gears\Nis better than any other car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.15,0:14:22.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The strongest car on the circuit is also\Nthe fastest on the public street!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:30.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The emblem on the rear is from\Nthe R of the unbeatable legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:32.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Can you keep up with my R?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Iketani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:42.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:45.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:52.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Takumi an unusual Road Racer\Nwho's only fast on Akina's downhill?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:56.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how he'd drive\Non other downhills.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:58.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you thought about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:02.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm very curious about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But for now, this battle is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:06.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be defeated, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:07.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:28.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Incredible.\NMy eyes can't focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:34.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Now he's getting serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:37.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's started grabbing the\Ngutter with the inner tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:44.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That's it.  That's the technique\NI lost to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I never thought I'd be\Nable to see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:57.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}My brother's stopped talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:16:00.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He can't relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:05.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I've ridden with him many times, but\NI've never seen him drive like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:08.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's serious.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.53,0:16:11.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0400,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Akina Skate Ring
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's closing in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:20.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The Eight-Six is catching up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:22.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Fine then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:17:01.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Now that you have done so well, my prejudice\Nagainst a ten-year-old car is completely gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:05.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's a wonderful machine with\Nfirst class fighting capability.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:10.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I won't hold back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:12.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm so glad he's making\Nthis so exciting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:16.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I haven't been so excited since\NI switched to this car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:18:00.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He can't catch up with the 32\Nat the exit of a hairpin corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:05.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Even if the Eight-Six gains on the 32\Nat the entrance, the gap will widen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:13.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Nakazato's got guts, pushing so hard\Non the downhill with a heavy 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:02.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The Eight-Six is gaining on\Nthe 32 in a high-speed corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:07.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}How can he four wheel drift so close to the\Nguardrail going faster than 100 km/h?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:12.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's got nothing to do\Nwith the car's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.39,0:19:16.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}His brain lacks a few lugnuts.{tightening bolts.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:18.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If he makes a mistake, he'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:22.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I can see the secret of his fast driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Since the Eight-Six\Nis underpowered...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:27.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...if the car loses speed, it loses\Ntime picking speed back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:30.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}So he doesn't slow down wastefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:37.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Now I understand why he managed to\Nstay right on my butt like a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:11.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I can't pull away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.89,0:20:16.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The time he stays on my tail\Nhas gotten longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:18.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Dammit!  He's tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:38.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The distance to the guardrail is\Nabout 20 to 30 cm for Nakazato.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:42.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That's about right for most Road Racers,\Nno matter how good they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:45.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But the bumper of his Eight-Six\Nalmost rubs the guardrails...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:47.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...and it passes the shortest distance\Nthrough the corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:50.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's in a class by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:53.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}How can he perform such\Nprecise drift control?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:12.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I've been steering hard,\Nkeeping the ABS on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:16.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}So the load to the front tires\Nis greater than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:19.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's getting tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:48.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The five hairpins are ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:49.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:55.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where you were overtaken\Nwill be the key point.
